are you running in?

119
00:05:30,375 --> 00:05:32,083
And you think it's okay
to flaunt your love life

120
00:05:32,166 --> 00:05:33,541
in front of us?

121
00:05:33,625 --> 00:05:35,541
--College has changed you.
--You disgust me, meowster.

122
00:05:35,625 --> 00:05:37,166
Why are you ganging up on me?

123
00:05:37,250 --> 00:05:39,541
I'm just partaking in
normal student affairs.

124
00:05:39,625 --> 00:05:40,708
[FARIS]
You are so gross!

125
00:05:40,791 --> 00:05:41,666
--[MAYURI chuckles]
--I expected better!

126
00:05:41,750 --> 00:05:43,000
Explain yourself, Kyouma.

127
00:05:43,083 --> 00:05:44,125
[RUKA]
How could you, Okabe?

128
00:05:44,208 --> 00:05:45,750
[MAYURI gasps]
A message from Yuki!

129
00:05:45,833 --> 00:05:46,750
[ALL gasp]

130
00:05:46,833 --> 00:05:48,208
[FARIS]
What? Is something wrong?

131
00:05:48,291 --> 00:05:49,375
[MAYURI]
Mm-mm.

132
00:05:49,458 --> 00:05:51,250
She wants to know if
I'm around Akiba now

133
00:05:51,333 --> 00:05:54,166
because she has something
she really wants to show me.

134
00:05:54,250 --> 00:05:55,041
At the lab.

135
00:05:55,125 --> 00:05:56,166
[OKABE gasps]

136
00:05:56,250 --> 00:05:57,083
[MAYURI gasps]

137
00:06:08,333 --> 00:06:09,875
[OKABE]
In that case...

138
00:06:09,958 --> 00:06:11,333
...let's go!

139
00:06:11,416 --> 00:06:13,000
[DARU]
Why you dirty...

140
00:06:14,041 --> 00:06:15,833
[DARU]
This calls for all-out war!

141
00:06:15,916 --> 00:06:18,166
Leave no comment left untrolled!

142
00:06:18,250 --> 00:06:20,125
"Normals Must Die-P"
was never one of us!

143
00:06:20,208 --> 00:06:21,625
He's nothing but a damned liar!

144
00:06:21,708 --> 00:06:24,500
How could you marry
Parthenon, you fraud?!

145
00:06:24,583 --> 00:06:25,833
[SUZUHA]
Cool it, Dad.

146
00:06:25,916 --> 00:06:28,250
[DARU] Whoa! @channel
and Twipo are on fire.

147
00:06:28,333 --> 00:06:30,458
--[SUZUHA groans]
--I bet those two get doxxed!

148
00:06:30,541 --> 00:06:32,583
I can't believe I didn't
know about this sooner!

149
00:06:32,666 --> 00:06:34,208
This is why you never
step away from--

150
00:06:34,291 --> 00:06:35,291
[gasps]

151
00:06:35,375 --> 00:06:37,666
[SUZUHA]
Listen to me if you wanna live.

152
00:06:37,750 --> 00:06:39,875
[DARU whimpers]

153
00:06:39,958 --> 00:06:42,916
[DARU] Suzuha, put that down
or Daddy will get angry!

154
00:06:43,000 --> 00:06:45,416
[SUZUHA] I'm already
plenty mad for both of us!

155
00:06:45,500 --> 00:06:47,916
[DARU sighs]
Right. Sorry.

156
00:06:48,000 --> 00:06:49,583
[SUZUHA]
Get it together!

157
00:06:49,666 --> 00:06:51,416
All you ever do
around here is nap,

158
00:06:51,500 --> 00:06:53,708
play games, and mess
around on the internet!

159
00:06:53,791 --> 00:06:55,166
[DARU]
Not my fault every time I start

160
00:06:55,250 --> 00:06:57,291
working on time
machines, I crash.

161
00:06:57,375 --> 00:06:58,416
Plus, we've already got one.

162
00:06:58,500 --> 00:07:00,541
