that as my template.

163
00:07:00,625 --> 00:07:01,791
[SUZUHA]
No, I can't,

164
00:07:01,875 --> 00:07:04,166
because it's the one you
invented in the future!

165
00:07:04,250 --> 00:07:05,625
If you saw it now,
you'd run the risk

166
00:07:05,708 --> 00:07:08,208
of creating a time paradox
and all kinds of problems.

167
00:07:08,291 --> 00:07:10,208
Well, if it's guaranteed
that I make the thing,

168
00:07:10,291 --> 00:07:11,333
then who cares?

169
00:07:11,416 --> 00:07:13,291
I'll get right on it! Tomorrow!

170
00:07:13,375 --> 00:07:14,541
[SUZUHA]
I am telling you,

171
00:07:14,625 --> 00:07:17,708
it is time you started
working on it seriously.

172
00:07:17,791 --> 00:07:19,625
[sighs] I remember Mom
used to get on your back

173
00:07:19,708 --> 00:07:21,458
for procrastinating like this.

174
00:07:21,541 --> 00:07:23,250
[DARU]
I'd welcome her on my back.

175
00:07:23,333 --> 00:07:24,833
Know what I mean? [chuckles]

176
00:07:24,916 --> 00:07:26,208
That's so gross!

177
00:07:26,291 --> 00:07:28,041
[DARU]
Yeah, forget that.

178
00:07:28,125 --> 00:07:29,291
[SUZUHA]
In the future,

179
00:07:29,375 --> 00:07:30,833
