that this world line

180
00:07:30,916 --> 00:07:33,625
is the worst one imaginable.

181
00:07:33,708 --> 00:07:35,041
But having me
was the best thing

182
00:07:35,125 --> 00:07:37,500
that ever happened
to the two of you.

183
00:07:37,583 --> 00:07:40,333
I came here to convince
Uncle Okarin that somehow

184
00:07:40,416 --> 00:07:44,000
we could figure out a way
to change the future.

185
00:07:44,083 --> 00:07:45,500
But since that day,

186
00:07:45,583 --> 00:07:48,708
he hasn't been back to the
lab and nothing is different.

187
00:07:51,125 --> 00:07:51,958
[SUZUHA gasps]

188
00:07:52,041 --> 00:07:53,083
[SUZUHA]
Someone's here.

189
00:07:53,166 --> 00:07:55,583
[footsteps]

190
00:07:55,666 --> 00:07:58,083
Uh, what are the
chances it's Okarin?

191
00:07:58,166 --> 00:08:01,166
It's not! I hear
boots. It's Mom!

192
00:08:01,250 --> 00:08:03,666
[gasps]

193
00:08:03,750 --> 00:08:04,541
[DARU]
You gotta hide!

194
00:08:04,625 --> 00:08:06,083
I am so on it!

195
00:08:12,083 --> 00:08:14,375
--[knocking]
--[DARU gasping]

196
00:08:14,458 --> 00:08:16,916
--[DARU] Yeah? Come in.
--[door opens]

197
00:08:17,000 --> 00:08:19,500
Hello, hello! How was your day?

198
00:08:20,791 --> 00:08:22,875
[DARU]
Ah. Amane, hey!

199
00:08:22,958 --> 00:08:24,833
What brings you to the lab?

200
00:08:24,916 --> 00:08:25,875
[YUKI giggles]

201
00:08:25,958 --> 00:08:28,041
[YUKI]
Oh, dear. Mayuri isn't here?

202
00:08:28,125 --> 00:08:30,958
Mayushii? No,
I haven't seen her.

203
00:08:31,041 --> 00:08:33,375
Oopsie! I think I must be early.

204
00:08:33,458 --> 00:08:34,750
She said she was
gonna meet me here

205
00:08:34,833 --> 00:08:35,916
with some of the other girls.

206
00:08:36,000 --> 00:08:37,083
[DARU]
That so?

207
00:08:37,166 --> 00:08:39,000
Do you mind if I wait
in here with you?

208
00:08:39,083 --> 00:08:40,416
[DARU]
Uh, no, sure!

209
00:08:40,500 --> 00:08:42,250
Perfect. Thank you!

210
00:08:42,333 --> 00:08:45,708
Um, is your little sister
out and about in town today?

211
00:08:45,791 --> 00:08:48,500
Huh? Little sister?
What do you mean?

212
00:08:48,583 --> 00:08:50,750
I'm sorry. Your little sister.

213
00:08:50,833 --> 00:08:54,416
Um, well, all of my little
sisters are strictly 2D.

214
00:08:54,500 --> 00:08:57,708
Uh--oh, yeah! You were
talking about Suzuha!

215
00:08:57,791 --> 00:08:59,250
[YUKI] Of course.
Who else would it be?

216
00:08:59,333 --> 00:09:00,625
Uh...

217
00:09:00,708 --> 00:09:03,625
--[sighs]
--Well... nobody?

218
00:09:03,708 --> 00:09:05,000
[door opens]

219
00:09:05,083 --> 00:09:07,375
Too-too-roo!

220
00:09:07,458 --> 00:09:08,208
[DARU gasps]

221
00:09:08,291 --> 00:09:09,458
Oh, there you are!

222
00:09:09,541 --> 00:09:11,625
Too-too-roo, to you,
Yuki! [giggles]

223
00:09:11,708 --> 00:09:12,541
[FARIS]
Meow, meow!

224
00:09:12,625 --> 00:09:14,708
Yay! Faris and Ruka came, too!

225
00:09:14,791 --> 00:09:17,666
[DARU]
Faris, my feline fantasy!

226
00:09:17,750 --> 00:09:19,416
[gasps]

227
00:09:21,833 --> 00:09:23,500
[OKABE]
What do ya know?

228
00:09:23,583 --> 00:09:25,041
Nothing's changed.

229
00:09:27,083 --> 00:09:28,250
[DARU]
Okarin!

230
00:09:32,875 --> 00:09:34,333
Mind if I come in?

231
00:09:37,000 --> 00:09:38,833
Hallucinations and
memory problems

232
00:09:38,916 --> 00:09:40,250
prompting the
Ministry of Health to...

233
00:09:40,333 --> 00:09:42,041
You don't have to ask
me for permission.

234
00:09:42,125 --> 00:09:44,333
It's your lab, isn't it?

235
00:09:44,416 --> 00:09:45,833
I suppose so.

236
00:09:45,916 --> 00:09:46,875
[MAYURI gasps]

237
00:09:46,958 --> 00:09:49,000
Wow, Yuki, your clothes
are so cute!

238
00:09:49,083 --> 00:09:51,166
I knew that's what
you were going to say!

239
00:09:51,250 --> 00:09:52,541
That's why I wanted
to show you.

240
00:09:52,625 --> 00:09:54,791
[FARIS whines] Do a catwalk
twirl for me, please!

241
00:09:54,875 --> 00:09:57,166
[DARU] We've got some sodas
here if you're thirsty.

242
00:09:57,250 --> 00:09:59,166
Wait, Okarin!
Where are you going?

243
00:09:59,250 --> 00:10:01,333
What? Can't a man use
his lab's bathroom?

244
00:10:01,416 --> 00:10:02,458
--[DARU sputters]
